data.description: Great opportunity with cul-de-sac living in this Centerville ranch! Located near so many things from shopping to parks and very quick interstate access. This home has all the high ticket items updated including AC, furnace (with air cleaner) , and water heater. Roof is around 10 years old and the home has newer double hung vinyl windows as well. Kitchen has nice granite counters and newer cabinets. Half bath near kitchen was professionally converted to full bathroom making 3 full bathrooms. New flooring throughout dining room, kitchen, and laundry room. Schedule your showing and come take a look!
